posts.content:
Grill-n-Chill 2016 promises more of the laid back, chilled attitudes that you've all grown to know and love.

It's a vdub event ran for the people, by the people.

We aim to keep it a family friendly chilled out weekend whilst making sure there's plenty for one and all to do.

We welcome ALL rides to our event from air to water cooleds, muscle cars, customs, hot rods and British classic. So long as you share our passion and have rust and oil in your blood you'll fit in well!

Two nights camping with three days show entry starts as low as Â£15 per adult with children under 16 free.

For full details visit www.grill-n-chill.co.uk or search for Grill-n-Chill on Facebook.

Hope to see you there.

Anton
